{"tid":1659642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登建議]希望各位支持同埋連仔入一入黎","createTime":"2019-10-17T05:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T00:12:32.000Z","uid":79319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"844e41f760b138a300c98f7e5ba5cb2a4eb3c3df","tid":1659642,"uid":79319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"起一個台叫「十八區」，入面有18 個或者更細既分台。可以比各巴絲打集中係黎緊既區內事務做討論，同埋普通市民可以集中睇到自己區內情況。我既用意大家明白，但因為連登不是為政治而設立的平台，所以我只係建議起一個比較有香港特色既台。如果覺得好既各位推推。多謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b276d246b2053e4017ac48c4044cc09a247140d1","tid":1659642,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bb8daa452ad1207652706a92c1582faf844796d0","tid":1659642,"uid":79319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"9e142fa0909e1bf701cd67d2e34942358afa93e8","tid":1659642,"uid":79319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:12:32.000Z","msg":"輕推"}]}